<h2>About Chicken Biryani</h2>
<p>
Chicken biryani is a famous Indian rice dish made with basmati rice,
spices, and juicy chicken. It is known for its rich flavor and aroma.
</p>

<h2>Ingredients</h2>
<p>
The main ingredients include chicken, rice, yogurt, onions, garlic,
ginger, and spices like cardamom, cloves, and cinnamon.
</p>

<h2>Why People Love It</h2>
<p>
Chicken biryani is popular because of its spicy taste, amazing smell,
and delicious layers of rice and chicken.
